# Backend Standards

Promoted from `.agents/rules/backend.md` (condensed).

## Mutations

- Sanitize on save: trim, lowercase email, strip HTML from text
- CRM changes → `CRMAudit` with old/new deltas
- Concurrent edit → `lockedBy` / `HTTP 423` where applicable

## Reads

- `.lean()` on read-only GETs
- `.populate()` human fields — no raw ObjectIds to UI
- Metrics via `$facet` / `$group` — not N× `countDocuments()`

## Imports

- Check-then-write / upsert — no duplicate leads

## Tenancy

See `tenant-security-guard.mdc` — `tenantPlugin` on models; `bypassTenant` only on allowlist.
